Hi,

 

Hope you are doing well.

 

We have compiled the most recent and comprehensive contact base of Technology Users. The contact base includes users of over 11,000 technologies, with key decision makers and designated executives.

 

Technologies: Acoustics, Applied linguistics, Computer science, Digital signal processing, Phonetics and phonology, Telecommunication, Sage software, Microsoft, Oracle, SAP, Cisco, VMware, SAGE, e-clinical works, Senior Software Developers, Web Designers, IT Auditors, Software Providers,  Senior Business Consultant ERP & CRM, Digital Engagement Director, Digital Marketing, Information Technology Planning/Buying, Business Development/Sales/Design/Development/Creative, Global Digital Services Director, Project Director/Manager, Digital Advertising Operations Director, Digital Innovation Global Director etc.

Kindly provide the below requirements to assist you further:

Technology Name  :            _____________

Target geography  :            _____________

Target job title      :             _____________??

 

Note: Once you give above information, we will get back to you more information such as counts, pricing and small sample file just for your review.

 

Looking forward to hear from you.

Regards,

Taimy williams

Marketing Executive.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

If you do not wish to receive future emails from us, please reply as 'leave out'

 

--
